  <brief_title>Impact of Omalizumab on Corticosteroid Use, Emergency Room Visits and Hospitalizations</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analyze the Impact of Omalizumab on Corticosteroid Use, Emergency Room Visits and Hospitalizations Among Patients With Uncontrolled Asthma Receiving High Dose Inhaled Corticosteroids</official_title>
  <sponsors>
