  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A retrospective database analysis to evaluate the impact of omalizumab on the use of
      corticosteroid, emergency-department visits and hospitalizations among patients with
      uncontrolled asthma and using high-dose Inhaled Corticosteroids (ICS) prior to initiating
      omalizumab.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
